      • add

        public void add(SharedBuffer.ValueTimeWrapper<V> valueTime,
                SharedBuffer.SharedBufferEntry<K,V> previous,
                DeweyNumber version)
        Adds a new value time pair to the page. The new entry is linked to the previous entry with the given version.
        参数:
        valueTime - Value time pair to be stored
        previous - Previous shared buffer entry to which the new entry shall be linked
        version - Version of the relation between the new and the previous entry

        Removes all entries from the map whose timestamp is smaller than the pruning timestamp.
        参数:
        pruningTimestamp - Timestamp for the pruning
        prunedEntries - a Set to put the removed SharedBufferEntries.
